                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Gregoire Pichon &amp;lt;gregoire.pichon@bull.net&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/70f3a49c-641e-11e5-bb7d-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/70f3a49c-641e-11e5-bb7d-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

